---
import MainLayout from "../layouts/MainLayout.astro";
---

<MainLayout title="Astrology">
  <section class="section">
    <div class="container">
      <h1 class="section-title">Astrology & Divine Guidance</h1>
      <p class="section-intro">
        At Kamadhenu Goushala, we honor the age-old traditions of Vedic astrology to offer
        spiritual direction, personal insight, and timing of auspicious events.
      </p>
      <p>
        Astrology plays an integral role in our activities, from determining suitable dates for
        Havan ceremonies to offering meaningful horoscopic consultations for devotees and visitors.
      </p>
      <p>
        Our goal is to reconnect individuals with the rhythms of nature and cosmic energy through
        authentic Jyotish practices, guiding lives toward harmony and dharma.
      </p>
    </div>
  </section>
</MainLayout>
